libsmacker
------------------------------------------
libsmacker is a cross-platform C library which can be used for decoding
Smacker Video files produced by RAD Game Tools. Smacker Video was the king of
video middleware in the 1990s, and its 256-color compressed video format was
used in over 2600 software titles.

Runtime requirements:
  cygwin-3.6.6-1
  libsmacker-devel-1.2.0-1bl2
  libsmacker1-1.2.0-1bl2
  pkg-config-2.5.1-1

Build requirements:
(besides corresponding -devel packages)
  autoconf-15-2
  automake-20250528-1
  binutils-2.45.1-1
  cygport-0.37.6-1
  gcc-core-13.4.0-1
  libtool-2.5.4-1
  make-4.4.1-2

Canonical website:
  https://sourceforge.net/projects/libsmacker/

Canonical download:
  mirror://sourceforge/libsmacker/libsmacker-1.2.0r43.tar.gz

-------------------------------------------

Build instructions:
  1. unpack libsmacker-1.2.0-X-src.tar.xz
  2. if you use setup to install this src package,
     it will be unpacked under /usr/src automatically
        % cd /usr/src
        % cygport ./libsmacker-1.2.0-X.cygport all

This will create:
  /usr/src/libsmacker-1.2.0-X-src.tar.xz
  /usr/src/libsmacker-1.2.0-X.tar.xz
  /usr/src/libsmacker1-1.2.0-X.tar.xz
  /usr/src/libsmacker-devel-1.2.0-X.tar.xz

-------------------------------------------

Files included in the binary package:

(libsmacker)
  /usr/share/doc/Cygwin/libsmacker.README
  /usr/share/doc/libsmacker/COPYING
  /usr/share/doc/libsmacker/README

(libsmacker1)
  /usr/bin/cygsmacker-1.dll

(libsmacker-devel)
  /usr/include/smacker.h
  /usr/include/smk_malloc.h
  /usr/lib/libsmacker.dll.a
  /usr/lib/pkgconfig/libsmacker.pc

